s class=\"obsoleteElement deprecatedElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strike\"><code>&lt;strike&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Resumo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>O elemento&nbsp;<strong>HTML <code>&lt;span&gt;</code>&nbsp;é um conteiner generico em linha para conteúdo fraseado </strong>, que não representa nada por natureza. Ele pode ser usado para agrupar elementos para fins de estilo (usando os atributos&nbsp;<code>class</code> ou&nbsp;<code>id</code>&nbsp;), ou para compartilhar valores de atributos como <code>lang</code>. Ele deve ser usado somente quando nenhum outro elemento semântico for apropriado. <code>&lt;span&gt;</code>&nbsp;é muito parecido com o elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a> , entretando &nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a> é um elemento de nível de bloco enquanto <code>&lt;span&gt;</code>&nbsp;é um elemento em linha.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"usage_context","title":"Contexto de Uso","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Categorias de conteúdo</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Flow content\">Flow content</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Phrasing content\">phrasing content</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Conteúdo permitido</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Phrasing content\">Phrasing content</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Omissão de Tag&nbsp;</td>\n   <td>Nenhum, deve ter tanto tag de início quanto tag final.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Elementos pai permitidos</td>\n   <td>Qualquer elemento que aceite <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/HTML/Content_categories#Phrasing_content\">phrasing content</a>, ou&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/HTML/Content_categories#Flow_content\">flow content</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Padrões de documento</td>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html5/text-level-semantics.html#the-span-element\" title=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/html5/text-level-semantics.html#the-span-element&quot;\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5, section 4.6.24</a>; <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html401/struct/global.html#edef-SPAN\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 4.01, section 7.5.4</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attributes","title":"Atributos","isH3":false,"content":"<p><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">Esse elemento inclui apenas os </span><a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Global_attributes\" style=\"line-height: 21px;\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes\">a</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Global_attributes\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/HTML/Global_attributes\">tributos globais</a><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">.</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"dom_interface","title":"DOM interface","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Este elemento implementa a interface&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSpanElement\" title=\"HTMLSpanElement\">HTMLSpanElement</a></code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Exemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:html;gutter:false notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Some text<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"result","title":"Resultado","isH3":true,"content":"<p><span>Some text</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/semantics.html#the-span-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;span&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/text-level-semantics.html#the-span-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;span&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>A interface com o DOM agora é <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLSpanElement\"><code>HTMLSpanElement</code></a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html401/struct/global.html#edef-SPAN\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 4.01 Specification<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;span&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.span","dataURL":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Elemento HTML <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<div id=\"sect3\"></div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Resumo","id":"summary"},{"text":"Contexto de Uso","id":"usage_context"},{"text":"Atributos","id":"attributes"},{"text":"DOM interface","id":"dom_interface"},{"text":"Exemplos","id":"examples"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"O elemento HTML <span> é um conteiner generico em linha para conteúdo fraseado , que não representa nada por natureza. Ele pode ser usado para agrupar elementos para fins de estilo (usando os atributos class ou id ), ou para compartilhar valores de atributos como lang. Ele deve ser usado somente quando nenhum outro elemento semântico for apropriado. <span> é muito parecido com o elemento <div> , entretando  <div> é um elemento de nível de bloco enquanto <span> é um elemento em linha.","popularity":0.0035,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<span>: The Content Span element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"span","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<span>","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<span>","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":